response.original_title: Extremely Dangerous Women of Wrestling, Vol. 1
response.overview: Spawned in the banquet rooms, fire halls and nightclubs on the east coast, dangerous women of wrestling gave birth to some of the wildest wrestling events ever. The highly contagious mix of former WWE, ECW and WCW stars proved to be explosive. The action is intense and hardcore. Anything goes matches featuring tables, ladders, chairs, light bulbs and blood!
response.tagline: Welcome to the World of Hardcore Women's Wrestling
response.title: Extremely Dangerous Women of Wrestling, Vol. 1
